            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e8801f1d959ec96b-0371ff twpub-e8801f1d959ec96b-05227b twpub-e8801f1d959ec96b-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>(*10) The <i>Epidendron, Flos Aeris,</i> of the family of the <i>Orchideae</i>, grows with merely the surface of its roots attached to a tree or other object, from which it derives no nutriment—subsisting altogether upon air.</p></div></div>"
        },
